  "title": "Sales & Marketing Associate",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are looking for driven individuals to represent our clients through <strong>face-to-face sales and event marketing activities</strong>. This role involves engaging customers directly at <strong>events, roadshows, and on-ground campaigns</strong>.</p><p>This position is offered on an <strong>independent contractor basis</strong> and is <strong>not an employment role</strong>. No online marketing or social media work is required.</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Conduct face-to-face sales and marketing at events and promotions</p></li><li><p>Engage customers professionally and explain products or services clearly</p></li><li><p>Build rapport and maintain a positive brand image</p></li><li><p>Achieve individual and team performance targets</p></li><li><p>Attend product training and on-ground coaching sessions</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Comfortable with face-to-face communication</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work in event or roadshow environments</p></li><li><p>No prior experience required (training provided)</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Performance-based earnings</p></li><li><p>Structured training and mentorship</p></li><li><p>Clear growth and leadership development opportunities</p></li><li><p>Exposure to real-world sales and marketing experience</p></li></ul>",
